metadata.name: Candy Vase Club Burn Token
metadata.description: burn 4 BURN TOKENS to get Candy Vase Club PFP, Candy Club Genesis is an art focused, passion project by two brothers, Nicky and Frankie, who have worked for Disney, Marvel, Sesame Street and more. Each Candy Vase is a combination of animated and still NFTs, based on which ranking you get!
